'''托尼·罗德姆'''，全名'''安托尼·迪恩·罗德姆'''（{{lang-en|Anthony Dean Rodham}}，{{bd|1954年|8月8日|2019年6月7日||catIdx=Rodham, Tony}}）是[[美国|美国]]商人及政治顾问。生於[[美國|美國]][[芝加哥市|芝加哥市]]，是美国前[[第一夫人|第一夫人]][[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]的弟弟。

==早年生活及教育==
1954年8月8日，托尼出生于美国芝加哥<ref>{{cite news|title=Tony Rodham, the youngest brother of Hillary Clinton, dies at 64|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/tony-rodham-the-youngest-brother-of-hillary-clinton-dies-at-64/2019/06/09/98ca3dba-8b01-11e9-adf3-f70f78c156e8_story.html|access-date=June 10, 2019|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=[[Nash_Holdings|Nash Holdings]]|date=June 9, 2019|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211142640/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/tony-rodham-the-youngest-brother-of-hillary-clinton-dies-at-64/2019/06/09/98ca3dba-8b01-11e9-adf3-f70f78c156e8_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=43|title=First Lady Biography: Hillary Clinton|work=[[First_Ladies_National_Historic_Site|National First Ladies' Library]]|publisher=[[National_Park_Service|National Park Service]]|location=[[Canton,_Ohio|Canton, Ohio]]|access-date=July 10, 2007|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913150519/http://www.firstladies.org/biographies/firstladies.aspx?biography=43|dead-url=no}}</ref> 罗德姆在[[帕克里奇_(伊利諾州)|伊利诺伊州]]成长，父亲拥有[[威尔士|威尔士]]及[[英格兰|英格兰]]的血统，<ref name="nehgs">{{cite web|last=Roberts|first=Gary Boyd|url=http://www.americanancestors.org/ancestry-of-senator-hillary-rodham-clinton/|title=Notes on the Ancestry of Senator Hillary Rodham Clinton|work=[[New_England_Historic_Genealogical_Society|New England Historic Genealogical Society]]|location=[[Back_Bay,_Boston|Back Bay, Boston]]|access-date=November 10, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607023135/http://www.americanancestors.org/ancestry-of-senator-hillary-rodham-clinton|archive-date=June 7, 2013}}</ref> He managed a successful small business in the textile industry.<ref name="Spet94 Chicago article" /> 而母亲拥有[[英格兰|英格兰]]、[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]、[[法裔加拿大人|法裔加拿大]]及[[威尔士|威尔士]]的血统。<ref name="nehgs" /><ref>{{cite news|author-link=Megan Smolenyak|last=Smolenyak|first=Megan|url=http://irishamerica.com/2015/03/hillary-clintons-celtic-roots/|title=Hillary Clinton's Celtic Roots|work=Irish America|date=April–May 2015|accessdate=2021-04-19|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323062511/http://irishamerica.com/2015/03/hillary-clintons-celtic-roots/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的两兄姐都是知名人物，分别为[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]及{{link-en|休伊·罗德姆|Hugh Edwin Rodham}}<ref name="Spet94 Chicago article" />

中学前往{{link-en|缅因州南中学|Maine South High School]]接受了教育。<ref name="Spet94 Chicago article">{{cite magazine|last=Hanson|first=Cynthia|title=I Was a Teenage Republican|magazine=[[Chicago_(magazine)|Chicago Magazine]]|publisher=[[Tribune_Publishing|Tribune Publishing]]|date=September 1994|url=http://www.chicagomag.com/Chicago-Magazine/September-1994/I-Was-a-Teenage-Republican/index.php?cparticle=1&siarticle=0#artanc|access-date=September 20, 2009|quote=The "boys," as they're still called, are Hughie and Tony ... At Maine South, the boys were known as fun-loving jocks. The Rodhams expected them to perform as well on the football field as Hillary did in the classroom|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930071005/https://www.chicagomag.com/Chicago-Magazine/September-1994/I-Was-a-Teenage-Republican/index.php?cparticle=1&siarticle=0#artanc|dead-url=no}}</ref>

罗德姆毕业后就前往{{link-en|爱荷华卫斯理学院|Iowa Wesleyan College}}及[[阿肯色大学|阿肯色大学]]读书，但他没有得到任何一个文凭，甚至是学士也都没有拿到。<ref name="cnnbio">{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1996/candidates/democrat/clinton/rodham.shtml | title=The Rodham Family Biography | access-date=July 8, 2007 | publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] | archive-date=2017-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811224144/http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1996/candidates/democrat/clinton/rodham.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==个人生活==
1992年与妮可·博克瑟交往，并在1994年5月28日在白宫举行婚礼，此为白宫自1971年时任总统尼克松的长女结婚后首次举行婚礼。两人育有一子名为扎卡里。2000年，双方分居并在隔年离婚。2005年再度与梅根·马登，目前育有一对子女。
==事件==
2017年11月，32名中国人曾将罗德姆及弗吉尼亚州州长特里·麦考利夫（Terry McAuliffe）告上法庭，二人被指控以“可帮助中国投资人取得绿卡”为饵实施诈骗，导致这些中国投资者每人被骗56万美元，并面临被美国驱逐出境的境遇。
原告称，麦考利夫和罗德姆多次到中国寻找投资人，借由他们分别是美国前国务卿希拉里的兄弟、克林顿的小舅子，以及弗吉尼亚州州长的身份，让中国投资者产生了信任。原告声称，被告利用这些关系向投资者保证有能力使移民局批准签证申请。
==死亡==
2019年6月7日，希拉里在[[Twitter|Twitter]]宣布胞弟离世的消息，死因未公开。

